<br>
(ooc) I guess what I am driving at, Tim, is if you do decide to play DAoC it would make me most honoured if you were to join Grymwyll and Ezmeres on the Percival server in the realm of Albion.  Grymwyll is in a young small guild ( only 10 strong) who looks to become more involved ( eventually) in raids and RVR... the guild, The Order of the Old Code, is headed by Voltare Dumonde who would have fit in the &quot;Menage&quot; mentality had he played EQ on the Brell server.  <br>
