<br>
Since I am not one who is a powerleveller, nor one who builds an army in one or two days, I feel as though those of you who are interested in the Steel Menage to play DAoC have a most open invitation to join Grymwyll in building as &quot;Menage&quot; strike force! <br>
<br>
The Old Code needs virtuous and selfless folk who enjoy roleplaying so to Tim, (and others of course) I give a call to arms!  Ye fayte o' Albion rests upon thee!<br>
<br>
<br>
Blair, (an absent but still proud member of the Steel Menage)<br>
